  "informal_statement": "The dot product of (a,b) with its 90-degree rotation (b,-a) is zero, i.e. they are perpendicular.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "The cross terms cancel; `ring`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem perp_rotation (a b : ℝ) : a * b + b * (-a) = 0",
